raw_text: COLLINS LEO MILROY peacefully passed away on 9 Nov. 2023. Cherished husband of Lourdes,​ beloved father of Sharon,​ father-in-law of Eugene,​ son of late James and Emily,​ brother of late Ranjini,​ Sherwin,​ Desmond,​ Premilla & Nirupa,​ son-in-law of late Xavier & Agnes. Burial in Auckland on 14 November.074115

TILLEKERATNE,​ LASANTHIE THERESE – Beloved wife of Nelson Tillekeratne,​ loving mother of Nishani and Ashley,​ affectionate grandmother of Tanaka,​ loving sister of Melitus,​ beloved daughter of late Mr and Mrs Kulasekera,​ expired. Remains lie at “Mont Calm”,​ No. 203,​ Galahitiyawa,​ Ganemulla. Funeral takes place on 15th Wednesday at 3.00 p.m. at Tibbotugoda Church Cemetery,​ Ganemulla. Friends and relations,​ please accept this intimation.074193
